{
  "stem": "23832.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's how people are-- some are murderers and the others are decent.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the other one was kind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He directed me when to get off.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] A normal, kind human being.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So I stepped down, and I didn't know where to go, but I was walking.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there was a woman, and I asked her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So then I left her and I was walking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was a policeman, and he directed me as to where to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I came there, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this girl was a-- like a maid, a young-- a teenager maid.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I forgot to-- did I tell you when I was to leave the ghetto, I put on me so many pairs of stockings, one on top of the other?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they said when you-- when they catch you carrying extra thing, that means you are a runner away from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I put on me a summer dress-- cotton with short sleeves, on top a black wool dress with long sleeves, just in case, on top a suit like you wear, a couple of sweaters, one like you wear a sweater, the other one tied-- hanging on the back and tied in the front, another one to cover me in the front and tie the sleeves in the back.",
      "word_count": 69
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on top of it, I put a-- they used to call it duster.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's like a raincoat-- a light raincoat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's how I left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had-- I didn't want to be accused that I'm a lady.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I put-- my husband had these big handkerchiefs in color, and I put like I am a worker, go to work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I left?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "August 28, 1942.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
